jade.core.security

Class SecurityService

  • java.lang.Object
    • jade.core.BaseService
      • jade.core.security.SecurityService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    jade.core.Service

    public class SecurityService
extends jade.core.BaseService
    ServiceService does not have filters, it provides the authentication mechanism and the SecurityHelper for performing common security operations.
    Version:
    $Date: 2009-08-26 09:30:57 +0200 (mer, 26 ago 2009) $ $Revision: 1708 $
